# CloudSchool Landing Page - Django Conversion

This is a complete conversion of the React/Next.js CloudSchool landing page to vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for Django integration.

## ğŸ“ Files Included

1. **base.html** - Complete HTML template with Django template tags
2. **styles.css** - All CSS styles (matches original design exactly)
3. **main.js** - All JavaScript functionality
4. **DJANGO_SETUP.md** - Detailed Django integration guide
5. **TAILWIND_REFERENCE.js** - Color scheme and design system reference

